message:
[REFACTOR] Verifiers abstracted

Verifiers for rounds are abstraced. This is done to ensure a uniform
treatment of the verification process.

Build info

The build info i.e. image representing status, from Travis CI is
added to the README.md.

.travis.yml added

The [Travis CI](http://travis-ci.org/ "Travis CI Homepage") uses
a .travis.yml page to figure out what to do with a project.
